ruvms 0.1.0
  • Get started
  • Reference

Proteomics data as raw LFQ intensities on the Sydney Heart Bank (SHB) cohort.

Source: R/data.R
raw.Rd

LFQ intensities of the SHB proteomics data set with sample information.

data("shb", package = "ruvms")

Format

Matrix of raw LFQ intensities with sample information as a data frame.

raw

LFQ intensities.

smpinfo

Sample information.

References

Li, M., Parker, B. L., Pearson, E., Hunter, B., Cao, J., Koay, Y. C., ... & O’Sullivan, J. F. (2020). Core functional nodes and sex-specific pathways in human ischaemic and dilated cardiomyopathy. Nature communications, 11(1), 1-12.

data("shb", package = "ruvms")
